title: Is Paco a hanging fish?
subtitle: How the red belly biscuits, mostly a vegetarian cousin with teeth similar to human teeth, gained a reputation for biting men's nuts.
author: David Emery
vclaim: The red biscuits, a gas type associated with berana but with teeth similar to human teeth, are known to have bitten men ' s testicles, resulting in the death of at least two victims.
